			  	McManus, in case you didn't realise, they have had an auto pact tool in the Game since a reset or two ago...it is under Diplomacy&gt;Management i think. Or click on Diplomacy&gt;status list, and at the bottom of the status list there is a clickable link which takes you to the management. in the bottom of the management page, their is a box where you can check it to accept pacts, truces, or allies, and it will do that whenever people send them to you. Also, you can click on all the members you want and offer pacts, allies, truces or declare war. Much better then auto-pact ever was since it accepts the diplo messages people send you whenever you aren't online.<br />
